---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Dental Bridges in Footscray | Seamless Solutions for Missing Teeth"
  description="Close gaps in your smile with custom dental bridges from Top Dentists Footscray. Our expert team designs bridges that restore function and aesthetics, blending perfectly with your natural teeth."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-background">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <nav class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-6">
          <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2">
            <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors">Home</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li><a href="/services" class="hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors">Services</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li class="text-neutral-800 font-medium">Bridges</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <h1 class="text-h1 font-heading font-bold text-neutral-800">
            Dental Bridges
          </h1>
          
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              Missing teeth can affect your ability to chew, speak clearly, and smile confidently. Dental bridges provide a permanent solution to replace one or more missing teeth.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              A bridge consists of two or more crowns that anchor an artificial tooth (pontic) in the gap left by the missing tooth(s). This fixed prosthetic is cemented in place, preventing surrounding teeth from shifting.
            </p>

            <!-- Benefits of Bridges -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg space-y-6 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-6">
                Benefits of Dental Bridges
              </h3>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Restore proper chewing and speech abilities</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Bridges allow you to eat your favorite foods comfortably and speak clearly without gaps affecting your pronunciation.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Maintain facial structure and bite alignment</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Prevents the remaining teeth from shifting and maintains proper facial support to avoid a sunken appearance.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Natural-looking replacement teeth</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Custom-crafted to match your natural teeth in color, shape, and size for a seamless appearance.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Boost confidence with an improved smile</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Regain the confidence to smile, laugh, and interact socially without worrying about missing teeth.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Types of Bridges -->
            <div class="bg-primary-50 rounded-xl p-8 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-4">
                Types of Dental Bridges
              </h3>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Traditional Bridge</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Most common type, supported by crowns on adjacent teeth</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Cantilever Bridge</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Anchored on one side only, suitable for specific situations</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Maryland Bridge</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Conservative option with minimal tooth preparation</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Implant-Supported Bridge</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Supported by dental implants rather than natural teeth</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Bridge Process -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg space-y-6 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-6">
                The Bridge Procedure
              </h3>

              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <div class="text-center">
                  <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold text-lg">1</span>
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-2">Consultation & Planning</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Comprehensive evaluation and treatment planning with X-rays and impressions</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                  <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold text-lg">2</span>
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-2">Tooth Preparation</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Preparing anchor teeth, taking impressions, and placing temporary bridge</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                  <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold text-lg">3</span>
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-2">Bridge Placement</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Fitting and cementing the custom bridge with final adjustments</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Care Instructions -->
            <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-8 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-4">
                Bridge Maintenance
              </h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                At Top Dentists Footscray, our skilled dentists use advanced techniques to create comfortable, durable bridges that blend seamlessly with your smile. The customized process involves preparing teeth, taking impressions, and precisely fitting your permanent bridge.
              </p>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-700 mb-2">Daily Care:</h4>
                  <ul class="space-y-1 text-neutral-600 text-sm">
                    <li>• Brush twice daily with fluoride toothpaste</li>
                    <li>• Use floss threaders or water flossers</li>
                    <li>• Clean under the bridge daily</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-700 mb-2">Regular Visits:</h4>
                  <ul class="space-y-1 text-neutral-600 text-sm">
                    <li>• Professional cleanings every 6 months</li>
                    <li>• Regular check-ups for early detection</li>
                    <li>• Monitor bridge fit and function</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Comparison Options -->
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800">
                  Bridge vs. Other Options
                </h3>
                <div class="space-y-3">
                  <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 text-sm">Bridges</h4>
                    <p class="text-neutral-600 text-xs">Fixed solution, completed in weeks, affects adjacent teeth</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 text-sm">Implants</h4>
                    <p class="text-neutral-600 text-xs">Permanent solution, longer treatment time, preserves adjacent teeth</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 text-sm">Dentures</h4>
                    <p class="text-neutral-600 text-xs">Removable option, most affordable, requires daily maintenance</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800">
                  Bridge Lifespan
                </h3>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                  <p class="text-primary-600 font-semibold text-lg mb-2">
                    10-20 years
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">
                    With proper care and maintenance, bridges provide long-lasting function and aesthetics, permanently restoring your smile.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-primary-500 text-white text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 observe-fade">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8">
        <h2 class="text-h2 font-heading font-semibold">
          Ready to Bridge the Gap in Your Smile?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-primary-100">
          Don't let missing teeth compromise your oral health and appearance. Call
          <a
            href="tel:96875050"
            class="text-white font-semibold hover:text-primary-100 transition-colors"
          >
            9687 5050
          </a>
          for a bridge consultation
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://apac.dentalhub.online/soe/new/%20?pid=AUTOP01"
          class="btn bg-white text-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-50 text-lg inline-block"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Book now
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>